| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5609 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 05dee109-8c07-5d34-8a2c-3e4517d689aa"
